Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:21.83,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)}Living through these meaningless days, I let out a sigh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:29.01,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}I've lost sight of my true self
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:36.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Even if I strain my ears I can't hear your voice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:43.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}So I keep walking trying to catch up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:50.91,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}The things I couldn't tell you form into a chrysalis over time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:58.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,300)}Spreading wings, they take flight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:06.00,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}The one, the one precious thing I'll never forget
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:13.97,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Someday, that warm emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:19.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}I'll do what little I can
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:28.57,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\c&H98ADF1&}Little by little, to get through to you
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.12,0:01:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky's really clear today.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.00,0:01:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.42,0:01:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a fried egg!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.00,0:01:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me back my protein!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.00,0:01:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.13,0:01:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Take pity on me! All I've got is a melon bread.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.18,0:01:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.76,0:01:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell whoever makes your lunches puts a lot of love into them.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.27,0:02:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how many times have you transferred?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.98,0:02:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've been tough, but you don't seem too screwed up.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.98,0:02:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nishimura.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.11,0:02:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've been a darn wreck by now.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.95,0:02:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh! I'm serious.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.99,0:02:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.74,0:02:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.37,0:02:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured if I let it bother me,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.12,0:02:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,they wouldn't let me live there anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.00,0:02:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think they could tell what I was thinking,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.30,0:02:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and they didn't like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand now.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.22,0:02:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have refused when they made food for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.51,0:02:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've just eaten it and told them it was good.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.11,0:02:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.94,0:02:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome back, Takashi{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.61,0:02:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you eat?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.78,0:02:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was good.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.66,0:02:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't eat your parsley.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.03,0:03:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But parsley's...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.03,0:03:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no good. Come on, eat it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.91,0:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:14.34,title-shadow,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\c&H678594&}A {\1a&HFF&\4a&HFF&}Place{\4a\1a} to Go Home To
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.34,0:03:14.34,title,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&}A {\1a&H00&\1c&H708EC0&\4c&H80ABD8&\blur7\shad1}Place{\c\1a&HFF&} to Go Home To
Dialogue: 2,0:03:10.34,0:03:14.34,title,,0,0,0,,A {\c&H035A08&}Place{\c} to Go Home To
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.34,0:03:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Master Nyanko{*Nyanko-sensei}, Touko{**-san} made you some pudding.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.68,0:03:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He went drinking again?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.10,0:03:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eat it myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.36,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.61,0:03:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it come to get its name back?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.03,0:03:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you, Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.42,0:03:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.46,0:03:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go anymore, Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.72,0:03:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.18,0:03:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.14,0:04:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him go!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.35,0:04:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It ran away pretty quick.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.77,0:04:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Natsume? Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You should rest tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.74,0:04:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go to the doctor first thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.33,0:04:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the supermarket and the pharmacy.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.45,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch over Takashi, kitty.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.92,0:04:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you suck.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.42,0:04:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you let a wimpy spirit like that get to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.15,0:04:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Master{*Sensei}?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Touko{**-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shigeru{**-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.16,0:05:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Master Nyanko{*Nyanko-sensei}?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.83,0:05:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's here anymore, Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.17,0:05:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I ate them all.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.13,0:05:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't start moving like that, idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.35,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Master{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.68,0:05:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and sleep!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.64,0:05:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember that demon!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.31,0:05:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You met it before?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.06,0:05:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, before I met you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.94,0:05:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't really understand demons back then...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.57,0:05:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I do now, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.91,0:05:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot, I don't want to fall asleep again...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.00,0:05:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have another dream...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.34,0:06:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked at me, didn't you, human?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.01,0:06:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eat you!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.35,0:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go home like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.93,0:06:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Up here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.89,0:06:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't see up very well.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.20,0:06:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.62,0:06:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see us, but you don't know anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you save me?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't save you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.38,0:06:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see him get pissed off.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.84,0:06:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Demons are all real jerks.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.26,0:06:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, what's your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.60,0:06:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.72,0:06:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you saved me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.31,0:06:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.82,0:07:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I'm late...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:14.71,sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.75\b1\fry4.77\frx2.64\fax0.05\clip(m 372.8 128 l 1272 25.6 1308.8 168 404.8 318.4)\frz8.995\pos(645.26,214.86)}I'm out shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:14.71,sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.75\b1\fry4.72\frx2.62\fax0.03\clip(m 372.8 128 l 1272 25.6 1308.8 168 404.8 318.4)\frz10.89\pos(657.34,276.26)}Watch the house.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She left the window open.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.05,0:07:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come in here!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.59,0:07:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.31,0:07:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.31,0:07:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Takashi{**-kun}, I went and picked up—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.98,0:07:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.36,0:07:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mom, did something happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.78,0:07:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.49,0:07:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.99,0:07:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... nothing.  I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The room was wrecked?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.80,0:08:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I don't think he's a bad kid,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.09,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's kind of scary.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.26,0:08:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should've just ignored that little demon.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.73,0:08:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobody else can see it, anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.52,0:08:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)}He doesn't have any parents,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and his situation's a bit unstable.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.57,0:08:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes, he just bursts out screaming. It's creepy.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.99,0:08:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobody understands.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobody.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never learn.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm an idiot.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.76,0:08:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Natsume Takashi{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.93,0:08:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.76,0:08:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.10,0:08:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you were living here,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so I came to see how you were doing.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.48,0:09:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And look at me!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.65,0:09:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to see you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.57,0:09:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Fujiwara Touko.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.11,0:09:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a distant relative of your father.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Out for a walk.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.08,0:09:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's dangerous to be out this late!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.83,0:09:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.00,0:09:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not want to?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.75,0:09:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.42,0:09:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.26,0:09:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.22,0:09:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.14,0:09:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her voice was very warm.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.61,0:09:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But was she really a human?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.07,0:09:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe only I could see her.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.03,0:09:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We keep running into each other.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.62,0:09:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is only the second time.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.67,0:10:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.67,0:10:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good comes of giving your name to a spirit so easily.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lonely, aren't you, Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.10,0:10:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the lonely ones.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.10,0:10:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fun to watch.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.73,0:10:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how I can stop seeing demons?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.03,0:10:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.45,0:10:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.57,0:10:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.37,0:10:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.04,0:10:47.04,number-box,,0,0,0,,{\be1.5\c&H2412C9&\fscx46\fscy45\pos(1760,1046)}\h
Dialogue: 2,0:10:44.04,0:10:47.04,number,,0,0,0,,{\be1.5\fay-0.14\fscx46\fscy47\c&H2412C9&\pos(1762,1048)}3
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.04,0:10:47.04,titlename,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\bord0\shad0\be1\1c&8A6424&\b0\pos(1198.47,1052.13)}Na{\c&967033&}ts{\c&A37D43&}um{\c&AF8953&}e's{\c&BC9663&}\hBo{\c&C8A273&}ok{\c&D5AF83&}\hO{\c&8A6424&}f{\c&926C2E&}\hF{\c&9A7439&}r{\c&A37D43&}i{\c&AB854E&}e{\c&B38D58&}n{\c&BC9663&}d{\c&C49E6D&}s
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:47.04,titlename-blur,,0,0,0,,{\p1\blur20\pos(1238,1079)}m 0 0 s 1350 0 1350 150 0 150 c
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.42,0:10:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can't wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.06,0:11:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.48,0:11:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... {*}Mrs. Fujiwara{*Fujiwara-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.27,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about the way we met last time.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.48,0:11:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about it,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.57,0:11:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and I figured you should at least know how we feel.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.16,0:11:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to come live with us?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.74,0:11:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We live way out in the countryside.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just my husband, Shigeru{**-san}, and myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.83,0:11:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Our house is old, but it's pretty big.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.59,0:11:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any kids, and it's a bit big for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.76,0:11:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard about you a while ago...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, you don't have to.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.18,0:11:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The choice is up to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.52,0:11:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you came, I'm sure our house would be much more lively.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.48,0:11:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shigeru and I will come to meet you soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.07,0:11:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So at least think about it, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder, is it okay for me to go?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.50,0:12:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She said she wanted me to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.04,0:12:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everybody else just took me in because they had to.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.34,0:12:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's the first one to ask me what I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.51,0:12:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's only because she doesn't know about me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.39,0:12:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to see her disappointed or scared.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.07,0:12:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.49,0:12:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to get you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.28,0:12:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay beside you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.95,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I like people like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.33,0:12:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A sad heart is delicious to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought that it might be interesting
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.96,0:12:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep a human as a pet.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.21,0:12:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.75,0:12:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.26,0:12:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lonely, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.80,0:13:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.94,0:13:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was stupid of me to talk to a demon.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.19,0:13:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It didn't follow me, did it?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.46,0:13:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't go anywhere like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget your scarf!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.76,0:13:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, Mom.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.26,0:13:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you wear it. You don't want to catch a cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.26,0:13:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then make sure Takashi{**-kun} wears one, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be off.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.14,0:13:50.35,Default - Overlap,,0,0,0,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.85,0:13:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's not here.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.12,0:14:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if there's some way
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.74,0:14:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to get rid of that demon before it finds my house.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.09,0:14:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's going to rain tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.88,0:14:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That cloud definitely looks like...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.68,0:14:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.22,0:14:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a scrawny guy I've never seen before.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.35,0:14:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A human chased me here from far away.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.85,0:14:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Must've been hard.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.48,0:14:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're weak, but they don't know fear.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.36,0:14:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way for a weak human like that to get rid of a demon?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.53,0:14:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell if I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.07,0:14:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, there's a hole for sealing spirits
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.95,0:14:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that a priest made up ahead, near the fox's boulder.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.54,0:14:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Some go to see it for fun—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.67,0:15:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I smell a human.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.17,0:15:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a human!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.39,0:15:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You tricked us!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.65,0:15:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.69,0:15:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.36,0:15:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.07,0:15:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.32,0:15:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I got rid of those weaklings.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.62,0:15:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you trying to do, Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.24,0:15:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.75,0:15:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been watching you this whole time.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.21,0:15:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no, it knows where my house is!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.58,0:15:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.92,0:15:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go together.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.34,0:15:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't live with humans, can you?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.92,0:15:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Some get drunk and hit you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.30,0:15:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Others conveniently "forget" to give you food.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.26,0:15:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And then those children say horrible things when they get together.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.43,0:15:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It read my mind?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.77,0:15:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong! Everyone was nice at first!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.98,0:16:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're good people deep down.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.11,0:16:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.44,0:16:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"They're good people deep down?"
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.57,0:16:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why aren't you loved, I wonder?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.07,0:16:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.32,0:16:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they don't want to let a freak into their family!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.95,0:16:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can come with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.29,0:16:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to go back to a home where nobody's waiting?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.63,0:16:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know this,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.88,0:16:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but if a human child disappears, it's a big deal.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.59,0:16:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll cause trouble for them.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.68,0:16:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.97,0:16:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just eat them all.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.85,0:16:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.27,0:16:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.69,0:16:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you go for today.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.48,0:16:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Say your goodbyes, and then come to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.24,0:16:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's waiting for me...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.33,0:16:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Takashi{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.75,0:17:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.63,0:17:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.96,0:17:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair's all messed up.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about my parents.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.68,0:17:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't really think about you, I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.93,0:17:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.85,0:17:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.01,0:17:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.39,0:17:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to think.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.98,0:17:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can I get away without hurting them?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.86,0:17:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.53,0:17:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would such a distant relative suddenly start to care?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.78,0:17:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Distant relative?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.57,0:17:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably going to ask for money later or something.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.70,0:17:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.87,0:17:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, it'll make things easier.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.45,0:17:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You were saying the same thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.42,0:17:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.33,0:17:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.08,0:17:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome back.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.00,0:17:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we have guests?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes... I'll get dinner ready.{added stutter}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.88,0:17:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They came.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.30,0:17:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{*}Mrs. Fujiwara{*Fujiwara-san} really came.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.56,0:17:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to go with them!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.77,0:18:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.69,0:18:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not going to disappear.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.06,0:18:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to say thanks to the people I'm with now.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.15,0:18:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, somebody tell me!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.19,0:18:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What, it's a human?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.69,0:18:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How noisy.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.82,0:18:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid brat. Let's mess with him.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.29,0:18:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me where the fox's boulder is!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.08,0:18:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I use the hole for sealing spirits?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.46,0:18:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this kid?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.58,0:18:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's human, but he's not scared of us!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So creepy!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.34,0:18:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.47,0:18:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm scared,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I want to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.43,0:18:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume. Natsume. Come out!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.77,0:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume, come out!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.68,0:18:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out now, Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.57,0:18:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A child like you could never seal a spirit.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.83,0:19:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd take care of you,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.20,0:19:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess you got too big for your britches!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.04,0:19:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to suffer, or you won't learn!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.55,0:19:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you... curse you!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.65,0:19:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.78,0:19:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One week in the hospital, they said.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.45,0:19:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What was he doing, going into the mountains by himself?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.62,0:19:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he doing it to hurt us?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.54,0:19:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.71,0:19:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I caused trouble for them again.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.96,0:19:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't go back to their house now.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.84,0:20:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my...  he's asleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.64,0:20:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to be quiet, or you'll wake him up.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.31,0:20:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.43,0:20:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Mrs. Fujiwara{*Fujiwara-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.23,0:20:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See? You woke him up.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.52,0:20:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were talking, too, Shigeru{**-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.02,0:20:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.24,0:20:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi{**-kun},
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.99,0:20:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,if you don't like it with us, you can leave whenever you like.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.12,0:20:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now, you need a quiet place where you can think.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.91,0:20:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Our place is as quiet as you can get.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.17,0:20:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.34,0:20:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't get up!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.59,0:20:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.47,0:20:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.06,0:20:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.24,0:21:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.66,0:21:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's mine.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.99,0:21:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad. He's mine now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.16,0:21:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up and go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.58,0:21:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not as interesting to you anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.54,0:21:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll give him sadness once more.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.71,0:21:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare a human disobey me?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.43,0:21:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He must suffer!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.89,0:21:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He must suffer!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.23,0:21:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The seal must have been broken
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.23,0:21:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,when the hole was dug up.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.56,0:21:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That spirit was stupid enough to get sealed by a little kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.86,0:21:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I got rid of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.20,0:21:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Touko will yell at you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.04,0:21:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Master Nyanko.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.38,0:22:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to go back to a home where nobody's waiting?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.30,0:22:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I have a place I want to go home to now.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.60,0:22:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're feeling better.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.31,0:22:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't you late?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.94,0:22:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, Takashi{**-kun}, your lunch!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.82,0:22:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.78,0:22:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat it all.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.36,0:22:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.16,0:22:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.66,0:22:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:41.21,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Lining up the sparks of warmth I've lost one by one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:49.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Coming to the rainbow-colored pieces of you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.39,0:22:54.89,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I crack a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:08.58,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Not even knowing how to make memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:16.25,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Even when we took things too fast
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:24.42,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We were only going with the flow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:31.39,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}No matter where I go, even after this darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:37.52,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}How many times must I say goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:44.44,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Shining with the flame of a young heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:50.70,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Those faraway pieces of you
